      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good starting point, but it's a bit generic. To really tailor the marketing campaign, I need more specifics on the actual demographics. Can you get more granular? I'm thinking about things like age, nationality, ethnicity, and even specific geographic regions or neighborhoods where they'd typically live or frequent. What does the \"face\" of this brand actually look like?",
