      "content": "Interesting. So you're saying the brand is basically limited to that specific Western demographic? I'm curious if you think there's any real market for this kind of watch in emerging wealth sectors, like in East Asia or the Middle East, or if those profiles don't really fit the \"ideal\" luxury customer you're describing?",
